snippet.title: Sophia Musik
snippet.description:
Donated via paypal  shoto1960@gmail.com
Cashapp
$ThomasSchoenberger
The only way to deal with an unfree world is to become so absolutely free that your very existence is an act of rebellion.
A system of morality which is based on relative emotional values is a mere illusion, a thoroughly vulgar conception which has nothing sound in it and nothing true.

This channel will provide endless inspection, or it will grow gray with abandonment.
It matters not. Fame isn't the end goal.
Epiphany is. For each of us. A personal epiphany.
I have taken the liberty to encode each video with ....a bit of alchemy...
Good luck.
